un route from Mar 29|work=The Hindu Business Line|accessdate=7 February 2020}}</ref> [[Dibrugarh Airport|Dibrugarh]], [[Dabolim Airport|Goa]], [[Lokpriya Gopinath Bordoloi International Airport|Guwahati]], [[Rajiv Gandhi International Airport|Hyderabad]], [[Devi Ahilya Bai Holkar Airport|Indore]], [[Jammu Airport|Jammu]], [[Jodhpur Airport|Jodhpur]], [[Tribhuvan International Airport|Kathmandu]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/transportation/airlines-/-aviation/vistara-announces-flights-to-kathmandu-from-february-11/articleshow/73239346.cms|title=Vistara announces flights to Kathmandu from February 11|work=The Economic Times|accessdate=14 January 2020}}</ref> [[Cochin International Airport|Kochi]], [[Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose International Airport|Kolkata]], [[Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport|Leh]], [[Chaudhary Charan Singh Airport|Lucknow]], [[Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj International Airport|Mumbai]], [[Jay Prakash Narayan Airport|Patna]], [[Veer Savarkar International Airport|Port Blair]], [[Pune Airport|Pune]], [[Birsa Munda Airport|Ranchi]], [[Swami Vivekananda Airport|Raipur]], [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]], [[Sheikh ul-Alam International Airport|Srinagar]], [[Trivandrum International Airport|Thiruvananthapuram]], [[Maharana Pratap Airport|Udaipur]], [[Lal Bahadur Shastri Airport|Varanasi]] |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.airvistara.com/trip/flightschedule|title=Flight Schedule|publisher=Vistara|accessdate=27 December 2018}}</ref>\n<!--  -->\n| [[Zoom Air]] | [[Agra Airport|Agra]], [[Jaisalmer Airport |Jaisalmer]] |<ref>{{cite news |last1=Qureshi |first1=Siraj |title=Zoom Air begins flights from Delhi to Agra, to add new routes. Details here |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/amp/lifestyle/travel/story/zoom-air-begins-flights-from-delhi-to-agra-to-add-new-routes-details-here-1614904-2019-11-01 |accessdate=29 January 2020 |work=India Today |date=1 November 2019 |language=en}}</ref>\n}}\n\n===Cargo===\n{{Airport destinatio